    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Omni-directional scrolling twin-stick shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The purpose is to control the enemy base by operating a combat helicopter equipped with a Vulcan cannon and lock-on missiles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is an arcade mode where you clear areas in order from area 1, and a free mode where you can play the cleared areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 7 stages in total.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is recommended to use a controller for operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move with the left stick and rotate with the right stick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vulcan cannons, lock-on missiles, and flares have ammo limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use flares to avoid enemy homing missiles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boosters can be used at any time and will increase your movement speed at the cost of fuel consumption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you get hit, you will take damage, and if the damage reaches 100% or more, you will crash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If it runs out of fuel, it will crash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no power-up items or repair items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268960/extras/e71213c8a90327a49419a011cff0eb9a.avif?t=1756417670\" width=384 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is recommended to use a controller for operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268960/extras/22785c32f4ec1bca519fe4d5e4b0066c.avif?t=1756417670\" width=384 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
